---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="footer">
  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <div class="footer-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>好奇你的卦象寫了什麼？</h2>
      <p>三千年智慧，一次占卦即可開啟。免費體驗線上占卦與 AI 解讀。</p>
      <div class="footer-cta-actions">
        <a href="/tools/divination?auto=1" class="cta-btn cta-btn--primary">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" />
            <path d="M5 8H11M8 5V11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
          </svg>
          立即占卦
        </a>
        <a href="/tools/divination?auto=1" class="cta-btn cta-btn--secondary">
          AI 智能解卦
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer grid -->
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-top">
      <!-- Brand column -->
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <div class="footer-brand-logo">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" />
            <line x1="11" y1="9" x2="25" y2="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
            <line x1="11" y1="13" x2="25" y2="13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
            <line x1="11" y1="17" x2="25" y2="17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
            <line x1="11" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
            <line x1="20" y1="21" x2="25" y2="21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
            <line x1="11" y1="25" x2="16" y2="25" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
            <line x1="20" y1="25" x2="25" y2="25" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
            <line x1="11" y1="29" x2="16" y2="29" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
            <line x1="20" y1="29" x2="25" y2="29" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
          </svg>
          <span class="footer-brand-name">易經研究所</span>
        </div>
        <p class="footer-brand-tagline">免費占卦・AI 解卦・古典智慧<br/>致力於將三千年易經智慧帶入現代生活。</p>

        <!-- Newsletter -->
        <div class="footer-newsletter">
          <p class="footer-newsletter-label">訂閱每週易經洞見</p>
          <form class="footer-newsletter-form" id="footer-newsletter-form">
            <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required aria-label="電子郵件" />
            <button type="submit">訂閱</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation column -->
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>導覽</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/">首頁</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">關於我們</a></li>
          <li><a href="/articles">所有文章</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tools">所有工具</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Articles column -->
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>文章分類</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/articles?category=經典導讀">經典導讀</a></li>
          <li><a href="/articles?category=卦象解析">卦象解析</a></li>
          <li><a href="/articles?category=爻辭探討">爻辭探討</a></li>
          <li><a href="/articles?category=哲學思想">哲學思想</a></li>
          <li><a href="/articles?category=實用占卜">實用占卜</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Tools column -->
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>占卦工具</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/tools/divination">線上占卦</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tools/hexagram-lookup">卦象查詢</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tools/divination?auto=1">AI 智能解卦</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom bar -->
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy;{year} 易經研究所. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="footer-bottom-links">
        <a href="/privacy">隱私政策</a>
        <a href="/terms">使用條款</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
